{"tid":2059603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強仔在獄中交代明天「放工」","createTime":"2020-06-11T04:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T04:58:24.000Z","uid":264165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90dd7509e3d837b94c8d28f1f943897f2ccc4fb0","tid":2059603,"uid":264165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"有關強仔在獄中交代明天「放工」事宜：<br />\n<br />\n1. 家長車已有，謝謝。（最後更新：12:50）<br />\n<br />\n2. 他擔心明天好多記者，由於強仔會有長者家長接收工，他不想被傳媒影到影響他們。如有傳媒想搵他做訪問，可以後天起（6月13日）聯絡麥潤培或譚家浚議員代為安排，強仔想安安靜靜休息數天。<br />\n<br />\n麥仔剛剛完成公務探訪，￼￼以上事宜是強仔希望公開的￼。<br />\n請幫忙轉達及轉發，謝謝<br />\n<br />\n麥潤培議員辦事處<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1495317374039477/posts/2613838042187399/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1495317374039477%2Fposts%2F2613838042187399%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=62e05d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1495317374039477/posts/2613838042187399/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YD49yfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYD49yfu.jpg&h=244aca52&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}